{"tid":466284,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我另一半竟然唔記得左今日咁重要既紀念日","createTime":"2017-11-12T11:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T01:58:16.000Z","uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0bb8fe1800a558e6e3bb42f311f1d5b155a5e1","tid":466284,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"我今年22歲 同男朋友同居<br />\n我地關係好好 佢都好錫我<br />\n咁今日就係我同男朋友同居第100日<br />\n本身諗住知佢鍾意飲咖啡 <br />\n就去左學拉花諗住比d驚喜佢 <br />\n慶祝我地同居紀念日<br />\n 點知佢番到黎竟然完全唔記得今日呢個重要日子<br />\n之前都已經比哂暗示同埋提哂佢我想要部iphone X架啦<br />\n佢最後竟然乜表示都無 <br />\n曬我一番心血<br />\n今晚決定趕佢出廳訓地下<br />\n希望聽日佢反省下知錯<br />\n聽日有番d表示比我<br />\n<br />\n我杯靚靚咖啡拉花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/12/195332_3d8e677f6c88f92454c2b4fc44bc4826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F12%2F195332_3d8e677f6c88f92454c2b4fc44bc4826.jpg&h=720f27fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd9cf7c16076dd79e2f0311d85c4a3be9efe72d8","tid":466284,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"出色"},{"pid":"85b34c6758eb7371470ba2613e5262702d86e7db","tid":466284,"uid":117821,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"拉花換部iPhone x 拉乜9咁撚貴？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 死臭雞"},{"pid":"3409597a6975ef3bff96910f6db5cde5263c22eb","tid":466284,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉花換部iPhone x 拉乜9咁撚貴？<br />\n<br />\nBtw 死臭雞</blockquote><br />\n我杯拉花放左好多愛心同我對佢既感情架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7c7c29d476f6ae169f24b85dedcd62b18e583b","tid":466284,"uid":12143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"200日暗示佢送層樓比你 到時唔洗趕出廳直接趕落街"},{"pid":"94315dc8b